title: Top 5 TEs! Andrews or Ertz? Who's #5? (06/25 Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Let's see what ADP is telling us about the Top 5 TEs. You can guess who the first two are, but how much better are Travis Kelce and George Kittle than the rest of the pack? And the guys debate Mark Andrews vs. Zach Ertz (6:15) ... TE Fill in the Blank! The Top 5 TE (other than Kelce) with the most upside (14:30) and most downside. The Top 5 TE we just won't draft (18:23). The Top 5 TE with the least upside (21:54) ... More questions about this group of stud TEs. Is Kelce over Kittle really an easy decision (27:45)? Are we underrating Darren Waller (35:00)? And the guys make their cases for Tyler Higbee and Evan Engram as TE5 in the rankings (39:00) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
